---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about SAUFEX - an EU Horizon Europe funded project combating foreign information manipulation.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-header__label">The Project</span>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">About SAUFEX</h1>
      <p class="page-header__subtitle">
        Secure Automated Unified Framework for Exchange
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="lead">
        SAUFEX is an EU Horizon Europe funded project designed to combat foreign information manipulation and interference (FIMI) through innovative research, educational programs, and international collaboration.
      </p>
      <p>
        We bring together researchers, practitioners, and policymakers from across Europe to strengthen democratic resilience. Our work focuses on understanding how disinformation operates, developing tools and frameworks to counter it, and building capacity through education and training.
      </p>
      <p>
        The project operates on the principle that protecting democracy requires a whole-of-society approach - engaging citizens, civil society, media, and governments in building collective resilience against information threats.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="media-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="wwd-header">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="objectives-grid">
        <div class="objective">
          <div class="objective__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
              <path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Research & Analysis</h3>
          <p>We study how foreign information manipulation operates, identifying patterns, narratives, and tactics used to undermine democratic societies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="objective">
          <div class="objective__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Resilience Councils</h3>
          <p>We establish and support resilience councils - local networks that bring together diverse stakeholders to build community-level defenses against disinformation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="objective">
          <div class="objective__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path>
              <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Education & Training</h3>
          <p>We develop educational modules and training programs for officials, journalists, educators, and citizens to recognize and respond to information manipulation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="objective">
          <div class="objective__icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line>
              <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>International Collaboration</h3>
          <p>We foster cooperation between European countries, sharing best practices and coordinating responses to cross-border information threats.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EU Funding -->
  <section class="content-section eu-section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <img src="/images/eu-funded.svg" alt="Funded by the European Union" class="eu-badge">
      <h2>Horizon Europe</h2>
      <p>
        SAUFEX is funded by the European Union's Horizon Europe research and innovation programme. Horizon Europe is the EU's key funding programme for research and innovation, tackling climate change, helping to achieve the UN's Sustainable Development Goals, and boosting the EU's competitiveness and growth.
      </p>
      <p class="disclaimer">
        Views and opinions expressed are those of the author(s) only and do not necessarily reflect those of the European Union. Neither the European Union nor the granting authority can be held responsible for them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="media-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-header">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Questions, collaboration inquiries, or media requests</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-card">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <a href="mailto:info@saufex.eu" class="contact-link">info@saufex.eu</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <h3>Netherlands Office</h3>
          <p>Alexanderveld 5<br>2516 BE The Hague</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <h3>Poland Office</h3>
          <p>Stablowicka 147<br>54-066 Wroclaw</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-cta">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/saufex" target="_blank" class="cta-button">
          Follow us on LinkedIn
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-2xl)) 0 var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .page-header__label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-purple);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-header__label::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .page-header__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .page-header__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .content-section p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .wwd-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .wwd-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .objectives-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .objective {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-light);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .objective__icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(107, 76, 230, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--color-purple);
  }

  .objective h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .objective p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .eu-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eu-badge {
    height: 80px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .eu-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .eu-section p {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
  }

  .disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
    color: var(--color-muted) !important;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl) !important;
  }

  .contact-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .contact-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-header p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .contact-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-card p {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-purple);
  }

  .contact-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-light);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-purple);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .objectives-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
